ProfessionalSummary:
I am an experienced digital marketing professional with proven success across digital channels. I have a deep understanding of
consumer behaviour and how this translates into innovative strategies and best-in-class campaigns, with a relentless focus on
the bottom line and future growth. My industry knowledge spans areas including finance, QSR, travel and retail, and have
expertise across all digital channels. I am looking for a new challenge in a senior role in a dynamic environment where I can
utilise my analytical and strategic skills.

Current position is a low-level management role: Digital Account Director
Starting on 1/1/2019, the candidate held the following low-level management position for 2 years and 1 months:
	Title: Digital Account Director for SPARK FOUNDRY (Publicis Groupe), Publicis Groupe
Starting on 1/1/2018, the candidate held the following low-level management position for 12 months:
	Title: Senior Digital Account Manager for SPARK FOUNDRY (Publicis Groupe), Publicis Groupe
Starting on 9/1/2016, the candidate held the following low-level management position for 10 months:
	Title: Display Account Manager

Positions.Description:
Digital Lead across a range of clients and verticals driving innovation and growth through strategic planning. While also
focusing on team and commercials for the business.

Achievements & Experience
•	Representing the agency in multiple successful pitches for new business, collaborating with group specialist services
to provide innovative solutions to prospective clients. Most recent wins include national hotel brand and EMEA
FMCG client.
•	Evolving Global FMCG brand strategy linking brand to ecommerce solutions, in our 'prime & prompt' strategy.
Currently presenting an end to end voice opportunity to senior marketing teams across EMEA.
•	Establishing our role to digital strategic planners closing the gap between comms teams and investment. Developed
role to more holistic overarching approach to campaigns allowing for more digital innovation.
•	Evolving traditional measurement and exploring new solutions, looking at attention as a metric rather than
viewability and traditional reach to deliver a new KPI framework across EMEA.
•	Working on efficiencies, cost savings and performance for businesses, achieved by using automation, proprietary
tech across EMEA to save team resource for up to 5 hours a week
•	Represented the agency at Facebook HQ for training & product brainstorms, gaining first hand view on new formats,
which I was able to bring back to my clients at launch.
•	Unlocking revenue for the business by up-selling the suite of solutions available, such as dynamic creative, across
display & social, content and ecommerce.
•	Unlocking betas and test opportunities for global FMCG brand across Facebook as a result of FMPA relationship -
includes mobile first creative workshops but also a Viewability Joint POV Project in Jan 2021.
•	Managing senior client relationships to ensure ongoing business success and growth via digital evolution. Building
hypothesis-driven testing roadmaps to provide foundation for developing digital performance, presenting approach
and results to senior clients.
•	Producing transformative responses in ever changing times. Planning and pivoting campaigns in reactive times
around Covid-19 working closely with clients in a pandemic.

Day-to-day digital AM for QSR, retail and travel clients including two of the agencies highest spenders, managing team of six and responsible for campaign management, optimization, reporting & client communication.

Achievements & Experience
•	Account lead for EMT, responsible for their largest campaign in their history, spending £1.2m in digital. Our media
helped to achieve their business revenue targets 3 months early
•	Rolled out onboarding partner, LiveRamp, for WW to maximise efficiencies and reduce wastage. Early tests saw an
increase CR by 33%, resulting in all channels adoption.
•	Evolving digital innovation, showcasing intelligent planning in line with new media opportunities such as developed a
bespoke targeting solution for EMT, refining data from their third party booking system.
•	Successfully rolled out dynamic creative across ASDA, EMT & WW on both display and social. This new approach saw
conversion rate increases of up to 40%
•	Digital account lead for display & social activity across the largest agency performance client, controlling annual
budgets over £8m
•	Experience in all aspects of digital media including attribution, econometrics, dynamic creative and data on-boarding.
Planning, developing and executing end-to-end digital strategies.
•	Building, managing and developing junior team across a variety of digital specialisms
•	Coordinating cross-channel responses to client briefs, ensuring collaboration across multiple teams and accurate
adherence to client timelines & business objectives

Responsible for a portfolio of over £3 million; planning, forecasting, testing and managing digital strategies for brands across a
variety of industries such as retail, insurance, news, cruise lines and FMCG.

Achievements & Experience
•	Launched Tango's first campaign in over 20 years, working closely with PR, social and creative agencies.
•	Early adopters in utilizing Facebook custom audiences to increase retention among existing customers with timely
upgrade reminders with bespoke deals based on their current plan.
•	Collaborated with talent from across The &Partnership on award winning Prince's Trust campaigns tackling issues
such as Domestic Abuse.
•	Represented the agency in new business pitches with success on Avon.
•	Running training workshops for clients in order to upskill and increase digital understanding.
•	Managing and developing three junior team members.


Platforms & Accreditations
Experienced tool usage across the digital ecosystem including buying platforms (DV360, Facebook Business Manager, Twitter Ads), bid management (   ~~~~~  ), ad serving (Campiagn Manager, Flashtalking), analytics and data
management (LiveRamp, Salesforce, GA360) and reporting (Tableau, Datorama).

Facebook Blueprint Accredited & currently undergoing Amazon Advertising Accreditation.
